I've always been doing
projects all over the world,

00:19:57.360 --> 00:20:02.290
and my partner comes
from Burkina Faso.

00:20:02.290 --> 00:20:08.710
And here are some
images of the city.

00:20:08.710 --> 00:20:09.990
Then there's the school.

00:20:09.990 --> 00:20:12.450
Very lovely to see that
wherever you go in the country,

00:20:12.450 --> 00:20:18.120
just before school people
start doing their homework.

00:20:28.010 --> 00:20:33.120
