camera that we develop for them.

00:20:52.530 --> 00:20:57.040
Here you see what the
school looks like.

00:20:57.040 --> 00:20:59.810
It's very lovely to see
how people have the urge

00:20:59.810 --> 00:21:05.900
also there to create and
to be educated and really

00:21:05.900 --> 00:21:11.910
want this to happen and
to give them a chance.

00:21:11.910 --> 00:21:16.770
And it's so lovely to see
that through art and education

00:21:16.770 --> 00:21:20.820
you can do something like this.

00:21:20.820 --> 00:21:23.810
Eri, as a little thank
you for the talk today,

00:21:23.810 --> 00:21:27.710
I actually brought you
one of these drawings

00:21:27.710 --> 00:21:31.125
that the students made.

